Biasanya begitu.

30
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:02,040
Karena hanya ada kita berdua...

31
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,400
- Aku mungkin...
- Tidak.

32
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:14,640
Peternakan Cumberland.

33
